<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Document Submitted for Verification</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #9B59B6;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .document-info {
            background-color: #f5e8f9;
            border: 1px solid #e8c9f2;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #9B59B6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>New Document Submitted for Verification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{orgName}},</h2>
        <p>A new document has been submitted to your organization for verification. Please review the document and take
            appropriate action.</p>
        <div class="document-info">
            <h3>Document Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Document Title:</strong> {{documentTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Submitted By:</strong> {{submitterName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Document Type:</strong> {{documentType}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>To review and verify this document, please click the button below:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Review Document</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you're having trouble with the button above, you can also copy and paste the following link into your
            browser:</p>
        <p>{{verificationLink}}</p>
        <p>Please ensure to thoroughly review the document and follow all verification protocols before approving or
            rejecting it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Document Verification System. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. For any issues, please contact system support.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>